modName: Fast Start with Save Games Dovahkiin
summary: These are the save games for fast start to game.
descriptionHtml:
[b][color=#ff00ff][size=5]
[/size][/color][/b][center][b][color=#ff00ff][size=5]Fast Start with Save Games Dovahkiin or Dova[/size][/color][/b]

[b][size=3]These are the [color=#ff0000]SAVE GAMES[/color] for [color=#ffff00]Fast Start[/color] to game.

You need only The Elder Scrolls V Skyrim.[/size][/b]

[size=3]You can fast start as [color=#00ff00][b]Dovahkiin[/b][/color] or [color=#00ff00][b]Dova[/b][/color]
then you can change name and everything on showracemenu.
[b]Quest[/b] [b]UNBOUND [/b]finished.
[b]Quest[/b] [b]BEFORE THE STORM [/b]started.[/size]
[/center]
[b][color=#00ff00][size=4]How to use[/size][/color][/b]
[size=3] Download manually and extract zip file.
Then copy or move which save game file you want,
to your [color=#ffff00]Documents/My Games/Skyrim/Saves[/color] folder.
Start Skyrim game. PLAY then LOAD and select the save game you want.[/size]

[b][color=#00ff00][size=4] Description[/size][/color][/b]
[size=3][b][color=#ff0000] Save 1[/color][/b] - Prisoner Skyrim (Going to Helgen Keep.)

[b][color=#ff0000] Save 2[/color][/b] - Prisoner Skyrim (Before given name.)
- You can give a name to your character or change sex or another.
- (Console command with ~ then type showracemenu and change what do you want.)

[b][color=#ff0000] Save 3[/color][/b] - Dovahkiin Skyrim (After given name Dovahkiin.)
- You can play with Dovahkiin if you want.

[color=#ff0000] Save 4[/color] - Dovahkiin Skyrim (After Alduin came. Game controls pass to you.

[b][color=#ff0000] Save 5[/color][/b] - Dovahkiin Skyrim (Choosing to go with Hadvar or Ralof.)
- Save 6 and Save 8 (Escape with Hadvar - Imperial)
- Save 7 and Save 9 (Escape with Ralof - Stormcloaks)

[b][color=#00ff00]Note[/color][/b]: You can choose later ingame. Imperial or Stormcloaks.

[b][color=#ff0000] Save 6[/color][/b] - [color=#00ffff][b]Male Player[/b][/color] Dovahkiin Skyrim and [b][color=#ff0000]Save 8[/color][/b] [color=#ff00ff][b]Female Player[/b][/color] Dova Skyrim
(After escape with Hadvar.) [b]Quest[/b] UNBOUND finished.
- Hadvar's uncle Alvor is the blacksmith in Riverwood. He should be able to help you.
- Talk to Alvor in Riverwood. [b]Quest[/b] BEFORE THE STORM started.

[color=#ff0000][b] Save 7[/b][/color] - [color=#00ffff][b]Male Player[/b][/color] Dovahkiin Skyrim and [b][color=#ff0000]Save 9[/color][/b] [color=#ff00ff][b]Female Player[/b][/color] Dova Skyrim
(After escape with Ralof.) [b]Quest[/b] UNBOUND finished.
- Ralof's sister Gerdur owns a lumbermill in Riverwood. She should be able to help you.
- Talk to Gerdur in Riverwood. [b]Quest[/b] BEFORE THE STORM started.[/size]
